<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.8.8">
<l>varivaḷaiyāṟ kuṟaivillāp perumuḻakkā laṭaṅkārai</l>
<l>yeriyaḻalam pukavūti yirunilamuṉ ṟuyartavirtta</l>
<l>terivariya civaṉpirama ṉamararkōṉ paṇintēttum</l>
<l>viripukaḻāṉ kavarāta mēkalaiyāṟ kuṟaivilamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except the want for [our] striped bangles</l>
<l>we have no want for [our] girdle that is not seized by the one of wide fame,</l>
<l>who is humbly praised by the king of the immortals, by Brahmā, by Śiva, difficult to understand,</l>
<l>who removed affliction from the great ground, blowing so that a flaming fire entered</l>
	<l>with great noise those who did not submit.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
